CBS Mail notices
================

CBS Mail is a custom Roundcube-based webmail UI overlay. It ships custom
templates, styling, JavaScript, plugin code, PWA assets, and branding files that
are intended to be mounted on top of a Roundcube installation.

Roundcube
---------

This project is built on top of Roundcube Webmail. Roundcube is a separate
upstream project and remains under its own license terms.

Project: https://roundcube.net/
License information: https://roundcube.net/license/

Roundcube describes the project as GPL-3.0-or-later with exceptions for skins
and plugins. Any copied or adapted Roundcube/Elastic files remain subject to
their original upstream notices.

Branding and trademarks
-----------------------

The Cybrense/CBS names, logos, icons, and visual brand assets in `branding/`
are included so the distributed interface works as designed. They are not a
grant of trademark rights. If you fork this project for another organization,
replace the branding assets, product name, PWA metadata, and trusted sender
defaults.

